    <legend class="f1 fw6 ph0 mh0">How much is your Alternative Minimum Tax?</legend>
    <p class="f4 fw3 lh-copy">
      If you exercise Incentive Stock Options (“ISOs”), you may be subject to Alternative Minimum Tax (“AMT”). AMT is a parallel tax system imposed on an alternative, more comprehensive measure of income than regular federal income tax with fewer opportunities for deductions. If the calculated “tentative minimum tax” exceeds the regular tax, then the AMT is imposed.
    </p>
    <p class="f6 fw3 lh-copy i">
      Note this site is merely to provide a rough estimate. This is not legal or tax advice. For assistance, please consult a tax lawyer.
    </p>
  </div>
</main>

